        <updateDate>2019-09-09T16:53:54Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Addressing Teacher Shortages Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Education (ED) to establish an Addressing Teacher Shortages Program. Through this program, ED shall award grants for local education agencies&nbsp;to address teacher shortage challenges. </p> <p>Specifically, grant funds&nbsp;may be used to establish or expand</p> <ul> <li>teaching residency programs, </li> <li>teacher mentor programs, </li> <li>specified recruitment and training programs, and </li> <li>other evidence-based strategies to increase teacher retention and support teachers.</li></ul>]]></text>
      </summary>
